OL,3,CSpring on pause: Arctic blast brings
OL,4,Csnow risk and a bitter chill across
OL,5,Cthe UK
OL,7,FIf the recent 'fools spring' convinced
OL,8,Fyou to put the winter woolies away,
OL,9,Fthen you've just fallen for the oldest
OL,10,Fmeteorological trick in the book!
OL,12,FLast week's sunny 21C will soon feel
OL,13,Flike a distant memory as Arctic air
OL,14,Fsweeps in across the UK tomorrow
OL,15,Fbringing a brief return to winter.
OL,17,FWhy is it suddenly turning colder?
OL,19,FThe wind! Or more exactly, the wind
OL,20,Fdirection.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774379485
OL,3,CSpring on pause: Arctic blast brings
OL,4,Csnow risk and a bitter chill across
OL,5,Cthe UK
OL,7,FThe recent warm temperatures were, in
OL,8,Flarge part, the result of warm
OL,9,Fcontinental air being dragged in from
OL,10,Fthe southeast.
OL,12,FIt was slightly cooler over the
OL,13,Fweekend and at the start of the week
OL,14,Fas the winds veered southwesterly -
OL,15,Fthough still a comparatively mild, mid
OL,16,FAtlantic direction.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774379485
OL,3,CSpring on pause: Arctic blast brings
OL,4,Csnow risk and a bitter chill across
OL,5,Cthe UK
OL,7,FHowever, a cold front sweeping across
OL,8,Fthe UK late Tuesday will see the winds
OL,9,Fshifting to a bitterly cold northerly,
OL,10,Fdragging in Arctic maritime air which
OL,11,Fwill dramatically pull temperatures
OL,12,Fdown both by day and by night.
OL,14,FHow much colder will it get?
OL,16,FA lot colder compared to last week.
OL,17,FHighs hit 21C/70F last Wednesday and
OL,18,Fhovered around the high teens for many
OL,19,Fover the weekend - but by the middle
OL,20,Fof this week, they are likely to
OL,21,Fstruggle to get out of single digits.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774379485
OL,3,CSpring on pause: Arctic blast brings
OL,4,Csnow risk and a bitter chill across
OL,5,Cthe UK
OL,7,FThat brisk, bitterly cold northerly
OL,8,Fwind will make it feel colder still,
OL,9,Fgoing below freezing across parts of
OL,10,FScotland and Northern Ireland.
OL,12,FThere will be plummeting overnight
OL,13,Ftemperatures too, expect some frosty
OL,14,Fnights ahead.
OL,16,FWill we see snow?
OL,18,FYes some will!
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774379485
OL,3,CSpring on pause: Arctic blast brings
OL,4,Csnow risk and a bitter chill across
OL,5,Cthe UK
OL,7,FIn air this chilly, the return of
OL,8,Fwintry showers are likely. The most
OL,9,Fprone spots will be across higher
OL,10,Fground in the north, most specifically
OL,11,Fthe Midlands and north Wales
OL,12,Fnorthwards, but there is a small
OL,13,Fchance of snow reaching lower levels
OL,14,Fat times.
OL,16,FSouth of the Midlands are more likely
OL,17,Fto see blustery, sleety showers rather
OL,18,Fthan snow - but it will definitely
OL,19,Ffeel cold and wintry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
